We recommended and the LCE agreed to instruct the 

(a) Accounting Office to (i) observe the proper accounting of BGCM transactions through the use of SAGF; 

(ii) use the prescribed accounts for inventories;

(iii) provide the above lacking documents and information; 

(iv) ensure future disbursements are adequately documented; and 

